// "EuroStrudelDance in Slovak" @by Enelg

setcps(135/4/60)


samples('shabda/speech/sk-SK/f:noc')
samples('shabda/speech/sk-SK/f:nikdy')
samples('shabda/speech/sk-SK/f:nekončí')





kick: s("bd:3*4")
      .bank("RolandTR909")
      .gain("<.7!3 1>*4")
      // .hush()


bass: note("<b2*16 g2*16 e2*16 f#2*16>")
      .euclid(12,16)
      .mul(gain("<0 1!3>*16"))
      .sound("sawtooth")
      .release(.1)
      .ftype('24db')
      .lpf(300)
      .lpenv(2)
      .lpq(2)
      .dist("1:.6")
      ._pianoroll()
    // .hush()


ohat: s("[~ oh]*4")
      .clip(1)
      .bank("RolandTR909")
      .decay(.4)
      .gain(.2)
      .hpf(800)
      .pan(.7)
      .pan(perlin.range(.2,.7).slow(3))
      // .hush()
      

hihat: s("hh*16")
        .clip(1)
        .bank("RolandTR909")
        .mul(gain("[<0!3 1> .2 1 <0!3 .2>]*4"))  //groove
        .mul(gain("[.2 1!3]*4"))
        .dist("1:.5")
        .mask("<0!4 1!32>")
        // .hush()


clap: s("[~ cp]*2")
      .clip(1)
      .bank("RolandTR909")
      .gain(.4)
      .pan(.3)
      // .hush()

snare: s("<~!15 [sd*4]>*4")
      .clip(1)
      .bank("RolandTR909")
      .gain(.4)
      .room(.3)
      // .hush()


synth: note("<b3@2 e3 f#3>")
      .euclid(16,16)
      .add(note("[0@2 <7 5>@2 3@2 5@1 0@1 3@2 <[7 2 3] [3 2 0]>@6]"))
      .sound("supersaw")
      .add(note(.2))
      .decay(.15)
      .room(.3).size(2)
      .hpf(200)
      .ftype('24db')
      .lpf(sine.range(2000,3000).slow(4))
      .lpenv(4)
      .lpq(2)
      .dist("1:.4")
      .mul(gain("[.5 1!3]*4"))
      .mask("<0!8 1!16>")
      // .hush()


speak: s("<-!3 [noc nikdy@2 nekončí]>")
  .room(.2)
  .gain(1.3)
  .mask("<0!4 1!4>")






// @version 1.0

/*
  @title Entering the lobby 
  @by BuboBubo
  @details Testing Strudel :)
*/

let chord_prog = "{Cm7 Dm7 Cm7 EbM7}%4"

p1: s("<bd [bd!2]> sd").bank("RolandMT32")

p3: s("~ hh ~ hh*2").bank("RolandMT32")
  .delay(1/2).delayt(1/8).delayfb(0.5)
  .gain("0.5 0.3 0.25 0.5")

p5: note("{C3 ~ C4 <C3 C2>@4 C3}%8")
  .sound("gm_acoustic_bass")
  .shape(0.3).room(0.2)

p2: chord(chord_prog.slow(4))
  .sustain(2).room(0.4).size(4)
  .vib(1/4).vibmod(1/8).voicing()
  .s("gm_celesta:4")
  .superimpose(n=> n
    .add(note(12))
    .gain(0.4).delay(0.5)
    .delayt(1/4).delayfb(.5)
    .arp("0 1 2 3".fast(2)
         .sometimes(rev)
         .fast(2)))

p4: chord(chord_prog.slow(4)).voicing()
  .arp("{0? 3? 2? 4? 5?}%8").room(0.5)
  .sometimesBy(.2, n=> n
    .add(note("12"))
    .vib(8).vibmod(0.25)
  )
  .add(note(12)).s("gm_reed_organ:2")

// @version 1.0
